# {{PROJECT_NAME}}

Built with [vinext](https://github.com/divkix/vinext) - a Vite-based Next.js reimplementation for Cloudflare Workers.

## Getting Started

```bash
# Install dependencies
vp install

# Start development server
vp dev

# Build for production
vp build

# Preview production build
vp preview
```

## Project Structure

- `app/` - App Router routes and layouts
- `worker/` - Cloudflare Worker entry point
- `public/` - Static assets

